Title: Announcing NuGet.exe and NuGet Client SDK Packages Support Policy: Keeping You Informed and Secure - The NuGet Blog
Description: At NuGet, our commitment is to ensure that our users have access to the latest, most secure, and well-maintained versions of our tools and packages. With this in mind, we would like to announce the NuGet Support Policy, a set of guidelines designed to keep you informed about the status of NuGet.exe and NuGet Client SDK packages on nuget.org.
